      "source_url": "https://ebible.org/engwebp/PSA040.htm",
      "text": "Many, LORD, my God, are the wonderful works which you have done, and your thoughts which are toward us. They can’t be declared back to you. If I would declare and speak of them, they are more than can be counted.",
